Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.n8tech.taskcan.Models.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    A User is a Task Requester and/or Task Provider. This class stores profile information, user's task's information and related methods.
    See Also:
    TaskList

      • User

        public User(java.lang.String profileName,
            java.lang.String username,
            java.lang.String email,
            java.lang.String password,
            java.lang.String phoneNumber)
        Creates a User object with contact details as specified by requirements. Two new TaskLists are created representing the tasks requested by the user and the tasks in which the user is a bidder.
        Parameters:
        username - unique username chosen by the user
        email - non-unique email address
        password - password set by the user for log-in
        phoneNumber - user's phone number -- must be seven numbers
